name: stempeg
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "stempeg" %}
{% set version = "0.1.8" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: f2266ad32d4e4ff3a936279b62a48ba58e6ada32f0e5ee53f4968877c0148136

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - ffmpeg
    - setuptools
    - numpy >=1.6
    - pysoundfile >=0.9.0

test:
  imports:
    - stempeg

about:
  home: https://github.com/faroit/stempeg
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Python tool to read and write STEM files'
  doc_url: https://github.com/faroit/stempeg
  dev_url: https://github.com/faroit/stempeg

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - Faylixe
